  %% Diagram 57: Vendor Onboarding and KYC Verification Workflow

  Start[Vendor starts registration]
  Register[POST /api/auth/register with locale and vendor role]
  KYC[POST /api/verification/submit\nNID + Trade License + TIN]

  DocCheck{Required documents complete and valid?}
  Revision[Send revision request for missing or invalid documents]
  Queue[Push to compliance review queue]
  RoleGate{Reviewer has compliance role?}
  Review[Admin/compliance review]
  Decision{Approved?}

  Activate[Activate vendor account]
  Access[Grant vendor dashboard access]
  Reject[Reject with reason]
  Appeal[Appeal or resubmit path]

  Start --> Register --> KYC --> DocCheck
  DocCheck -- No --> Revision --> KYC
  DocCheck -- Yes --> Queue --> RoleGate
  RoleGate -- No --> Revision
  RoleGate -- Yes --> Review --> Decision

  Decision -- Yes --> Activate --> Access
  Decision -- No --> Reject --> Appeal --> KYC
